"Katie" Pavlich (born July 10, 1988)[3][4] is an American conservative journalist, primarily known for her work at the online news magazines Townhall.com and The Hill, as well as for authoring the book Fast and Furious: Barack Obama's Bloodiest Scandal and Its Shameless Cover-Up.
